<title>黎真主党领导人最新发声</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E7%8E%AF%E7%90%83%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5+%E9%BB%8E%E7%9C%9F%E4%B8%BB%E5%85%9A%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC%E4%BA%BA%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E5%8F%91%E5%A3%B0</link>
